#+title: Browser Ideas

* Main ideas
- Edge like sidebar
- Split screen (like arc/edge/vivaldi)
- Vertical tabs 
  - All the best features from vivaldi/sideberry/tree style tabs/arc
- Spotlight search
  - Like arc/vivaldi
- Tab managment
  - Workspaces that are synced between windows and persist restarts
  - Tab groups (like vivaldi)
- Ui item position location customization
  - Be able to change the position of the tabs/sidebar/urlbar/bookmakrs ext
- Easily manage extension permisions
- Change user.js on the fly
- Browser available chrome.css themes and switch easily
- compiler optimizations
- Easy downloads 
  - Simple installers for macos/windows
  - Packages for all major distros
    - Arch
    - Debian
    - Fedora
    - Ubuntu
    - OpenSuse
    - Gentoo
    - NixOS
    - Bsd maybe ??!?!(FreeBSD, NetBSD, OpenBSD)
    - Void linux
- Connention to the tor network
- Vim bindings
  
* Browser to take inspo from
- Librewolf
- Floorp
- Pulse
- Arc(macos)
- Sigmaos(macos)
- Chrome
- Edge
- Vivaldi
- waterfox
- mercury
- Minimal browsers
  - Qute browser
  - Vimb
  - Vieb
  - Min browser
  - Gnu icecat
  - Tor
